Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.54,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.45,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.26,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:22.75,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:27.48,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:34.42,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time... all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would someday keep your promise to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you told me then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...you've come here so we can... die together...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...you said... we could die together...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mad! She's gone completely mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}14. The Secret Door
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not her! Look at me closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Fukiko-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's heavily drugged again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You said we could die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... here is the bracelet, still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It never left my wrist since the day you gave it to me... just as you wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So now... finally, you came to die with me, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing good to be said of Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, let us die and dwell together in eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is this... that nothing can give any kind of meaning to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama! Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not her! I'm not Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lend you all my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not her! I'm not her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! It's just me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, my Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked into Rei's deranged Fukiko-obsessed eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I think I saw there... something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...something more like love... than hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You said we could die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See, here is the bracelet still, just as you wished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And the scar... what if that scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...what if it is from a double-suicide attempt with Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama is out today, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it that I find you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What business would a freshman have here in a senior's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your absences from the cram sessions are becoming conspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'm sincerely sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be certain to attend from now on, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You must study especially hard right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you won't have time to be snooping around into other people's affairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pleasant sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...thanks to my little pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still taking these drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... maybe it would be wise to lock your door,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...at least when you are asleep, I would think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Any stranger, or thief, could come right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They can take whatever they want. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's slipped my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The year Shakespeare was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 1564... and he died in 1616.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy, just remember "He wrote many plays about murder." See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Hito goroshi?"{\i0} 1-5-6-4...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get that from the Sorority cram session?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I have heavy responsibilities, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure do. And lots of pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, do you have a cram session today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, from now on we do self-study only.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only five days left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Sisters have their own mid-terms to study for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's... let's study together then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You started doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing "Nanako has a secret."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:12.69,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Baroque music was played from the 17th century to the mid-18th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.97,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,The main composers in that style were
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:21.64,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Georg Friedrich Handel, Johann Sebastian Bach, and Antonio Vivaldi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, I'll make a cheesecake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then... I'll make something from that roast beef I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better copy that down! They say it'll be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-San! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw... I was hoping... that she'd help me with my French.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have come earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's this about Misonoo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... yes, she's just not been herself lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Daydreaming all day... not even a "goodbye" when she leaves for home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe my French will do, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you'll accept me as Misonoo-san's substitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! It starts on page 57...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? My cheesecake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The roast beef sandwich is good too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay the hell outta my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! I didn't ask for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate prying nuisances like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay the hell outta my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate prying nuisances like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but I just don't think it's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...to ruin one's health with drugs like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm absolutely convinced of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I won't be able to visit her apartment ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! I didn't ask for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been since I came to look at the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to accompany me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mid-terms begin tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You even brought that with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No more drugs for me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're calling me that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be about the doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there some memory behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that reflects from within those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How can... Who can possibly fathom their meaning, my Dear Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... oh... we met somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,From cram school. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Henmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, that was it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you... still get letters from Henmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... yes... I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? He hardly ever writes letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but do you live in this apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... no, a friend of mine does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Here it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good-bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your "friend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! My flash cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'll be okay without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,More often than you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better quit. It's not good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret saying this, but this must remain a S-E-C-R-E-T.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as late as hell! I thought I'd miss the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be late for the tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I still have so much to memorize!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakespeare... "wrote many books on kidnapping."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Tomoko! Not "kidnapping"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's {\i1}"hito bashira"{\i0}? No? What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to buy an eraser!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling well now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You showed up for the first day of mid-terms!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I force the teachers to give me make-up exams every term?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mid-terms have begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:14.16,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:19.63,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:25.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:30.71,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:36.99,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.99,0:24:42.46,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:45.19,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.19,0:24:48.00,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.00,0:24:50.40,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.40,0:24:55.67,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.59,0:25:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako is badly shaken to learn Fukiko's secret truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.56,0:25:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...regarding Nanako's admission into the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a Sorority party is held aboard a yacht,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.78,0:25:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Fukiko has yet another surprise for Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.36,0:25:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Fukiko; The Sea Rumbles
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.81,0:25:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
